data.description: Nestled in the heart of Norfolk's desirable Devon Manor neighborhood, this charming 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home offers a delightful blend of classic character and modern updates. Built in 1942 and updated in 2021, this well-maintained residence exudes warmth and inviting ambiance, making it an ideal haven for buyers seeking a comfortable and tranquil lifestyle. This property comes installed with a 60 AMP Power Line installed, Currently with a Tesla Home Charger, but can be easily replaced to any EV Charger or RV Power Socket. Proximity to the Base, Beaches, Breweries plus ease of access to East Beach,  Ocean View and Interstates to explore all of Hampton Roads this location make this home a phenomenal spot to land!
